"2017-08-11T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你超完都3.7不如用返default <br />\nDefault 個個會自己按需升頻率<br />\n打機就全3.7<br />\nIdle 就1.x<br />\n洗鬼超</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e91bf5a3d69d6029ef455138461142f1a2baaa7","tid":354653,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超同唔超 你feel唔feel 到分別先<br />\n<br />\n我用1700x ,超到4.0（5x度）同 預設3.5 （4x度）冇分別<br />\n平時降到2.0ghz用 都好流暢</blockquote><br />\n你用1700x 啫，我地用1700 default 得3.2，無成本(voltage都唔駛點加) 升上3.7冇理由唔唔超呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62657c60e3bb4348fa159ce1039cb95f88d79e1f","tid":354653,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"1700@3.6ghz<br />\nr1 universal<br />\nidle 32 <br />\n打機48<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b21193961def7fa86fad933a871cac71c83535","tid":354653,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你超完都3.7不如用返default <br />\nDefault 個個會自己按需升頻率<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打機就全3.7</span><br />\nIdle 就1.x<br />\n洗鬼超</blockquote><br />\n???</blockquote><br />\n佢會自己調架嘛<br />\n睇你打咩機用到邊個core 囉</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知1700唔超頻幾核先行到3.7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你打機用得幾核 比盡咪4核</blockquote><br />\n4核都已經turbo唔到上去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07a59a81177c6240538f72b8ec799a783331bda","tid":354653,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1700@3.6ghz<br />\nr1 universal<br />\nidle 32 <br />\n打機48<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你用塔散實低d既<br />\n不過用得塔散做咩唔超多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g