moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢粒u同板超唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.18v就上了3.6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndefault電壓都上到3.7</blockquote><br />\n唔准再笑青蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3.8樓下果啲唔好拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  電壓又唔洗點加又唔會熱"},{"pid":"fe147df13fcf3912d81af61a5f1307a86a8b0053","tid":354653,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"用水冷<br />\n1.4v 4.0ghz打機都係under 60度"},{"pid":"c52b42da4f5977544f2ec1dac90a0d4d4cffc50d","tid":354653,"uid":53421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用水冷<br />\n1.4v 4.0ghz打機都係under 60度</blockquote><br />\n比1000蚊整套水冷係最簡單既解決方法"},{"pid":"f89545e7222c4245b6adf7e4070785b3f6a654f7","tid":354653,"uid":39514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"1.31v上3.8用塔散 不過打機最高會標左去70度<br />\n遲下屎忽痕再降電壓睇下得唔得"},{"pid":"5c5c7633e3e0dcf6afb2f8cda0d94b7617c6e60d","tid":354653,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"超3.675 3.725 3.75 3.775可以降頻"},{"pid":"276da4bae6c4c24d117100dd4302b2b04e4d7f8f","tid":354653,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"唔好超咁多，降下壓先囉。"},{"pid":"dc8414618f4329aeaf2eea12b50e9150356890c6","tid":354653,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"宜家d人真係好貪心<br />\n又要馬好 又要馬不吃草<br />\n<br />\n原廠散熱 一定冇水冷同塔散效果好<br />\n而且你oc一定會熱"},{"pid":"5a6e1b319a5e6ed1218747b81ad432fe8cc3e14c","tid":354653,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-